”Alexa, open Nashville Explorer”
”Where should I go”
”Give me the top five”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: nashville explorer
des: Explore Nashville Tennesse like you never have before. Nashville Explorer can tell you about exciting things to do in and around the city. It can recommend great restaurants. It can tell you the local news, check the weather, and guide you to the city's top attractions.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
